<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10561915>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Wing venation of Uncobotyodes spp. A U. patulalis. B U. latizona sp. nov. Upper is forewing, lower is hindwing. Scale bars: 1.0 mm." ;
